===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|worste}}, {{m|enm|wurste}}, {{m|enm|warste}}, {{m|enm|werste}}, {{m|enm|wirste}}, from {{inh|en|ang|wyrst}}, {{m|ang|wierst}}, {{m|ang|wirst}}, {{m|ang|wirrest|pos=adverb}} and {{inh|en|ang|wyrsta}}, {{m|ang|wyrresta|pos=adjective}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*wirsistaz}}, superlative form of {{m|gem-pro|*ubilaz|t=bad, evil}}. Cognate with {{cog|osx|wirsista}}, {{m|osx|wirrista|t=worst}}, {{cog|goh|wirst}}, {{m|goh|wirsesto}}, {{m|goh|wirsisto|t=worst}}, {{cog|da|værst|t=worst}}, {{cog|sv|värst|t=worst}}, {{cog|is|verstur|t=worst}}.

